OL,3,CKing lays out government's agenda amid
OL,4,CStarmer leadership crisis
OL,6,FThe King has delivered his speech
OL,7,Foutlining the government's agenda for
OL,8,Fthe year as Keir Starmer fights to
OL,9,Fstay on as prime minister.
OL,11,FNearly 100 Labour MPs are prepared to
OL,12,Foust Starmer as the government faces a
OL,13,Fpolitical fallout following last
OL,14,Fweek's electoral losses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
