OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778681476
OL,3,CKing lays out government's agenda amid
OL,4,CStarmer leadership crisis
OL,6,FCharles said on Wednesday the
OL,7,FGovernment will "defend the British
OL,8,Fvalues of decency, tolerance and
OL,9,Frespect for difference under our
OL,10,Fcommon flag" and will take "urgent
OL,11,Faction to tackle antisemitism and
OL,12,Fensure all communities feel safe".
OL,14,FWatch the King's Speech Live
OL,26,@oD@QOUrD@LO]rD@\OUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
