PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778681476
OL,3,CKing lays out government's agenda amid
OL,4,CStarmer leadership crisis
OL,6,FHe added that the government will
OL,7,Fenact laws in response to the
OL,8,F"horrific attack" in Southport in 2024
OL,9,Fwith measures to "protect the British
OL,10,Fpeople from extreme violence, and
OL,11,Fhonour the victims, the injured and
OL,12,Ftheir families".
OL,14,FCharles wore his Admiral of the Fleet
OL,15,FRoyal Naval Number 1 Dress with cap
OL,16,Fand sword as he addressed Parliament.
OL,18,FThe speech included more than 35 bills
OL,19,Fcovering immigration, the NHS, police
OL,20,Freform, and the nationalisation of
OL,21,FBritish Steel.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@QO]qD@ROUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
