PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778681476
OL,3,CKing lays out government's agenda amid
OL,4,CStarmer leadership crisis
OL,6,FBut with Starmer's position under
OL,7,Fpressure, it is unclear whether he
OL,8,Fwill still be PM to deliver on the
OL,9,Fgovernment's agenda.
OL,11,FThe speech was written by the
OL,12,Fgovernment and represents the symbolic
OL,13,Frole of the monarch in the
OL,14,Fconstitution, through whom
OL,15,Fparliamentary power is formally
OL,16,Fexercised.
OL,18,FMPs will debate the legislative agenda
OL,19,Fand vote on it during the
OL,20,Fparliamentary session.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
