PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778681476
OL,3,CKing lays out government's agenda amid
OL,4,CStarmer leadership crisis
OL,6,FThis is the third time King Charles
OL,7,Fhas delivered the speech as monarch,
OL,8,Fthough he also stood in for Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth II when she was unwell in
OL,10,FMay 2022.
OL,12,FThe King was met with protesters as he
OL,13,Farrived at the House of Lords to
OL,14,Fdeliver his speech.
OL,16,FRepublic protesters shouted "free
OL,17,FPalestine" and "from the river to the
OL,18,Fsea, Palestine will be free" outside
OL,19,Fthe House of Lords as the King passed
OL,20,Fin his carriage.
