OL,3,CKing lays out government's agenda amid
OL,4,CStarmer leadership crisis
OL,6,FThey held up a sign saying "Stop MPs
OL,7,Ftaking pro-Israel lobbying money".
OL,9,FNext to it, another sign on Parliament
OL,10,FStreet said: "Don't let Farage +
OL,11,FReform divide the country."
OL,13,FThe largest placard read: "End Zionism
OL,14,Fcontrol of UK politics. Break the
OL,15,Falliance with Israel."
